    <p>The switch is used to temporarily  disable the water pump for 2 hours, if pressed. It will overwrite the water pump on/off schedule (see below)</p>
    <p>The power relay is controlling the water pump on or off. The pump on/off schedule is updated via web service call every minute. So if there is an update on the power
        pump schedule on the web server, it will be notified. Once the new schedule is updated, the power relay will be following the new on/off schedule.</p>
    
